Description:                               =
============================================

The Temple of Peace is in disarray: somebody has stolen the gems from the Tree of Harmony. Help your three little heroes Rob, Egg and Liz to find the gems again! Way to Go! is a game with simple rules and incredibly tricky puzzles. Just use the mouse to drag commands onto the tiles and guide your heroes to the exit. You can rewind at any time to correct mistakes. Way to Go! has over 400 levels, guaranteeing hours of fun.
